&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You will be thrown at different tasks and problems across the company and help support Avi Medical to fulfill its vision. This role is the best opportunity to learn directly from experienced founders and the leadership team in an extremely short period of time about how to build a business from scratch, how to solve any problem and how to achieve any possible goal.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are looking for a full-time intern based in Munich&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Support the fast scaling of Avi Medical and get deep insights into Expansion&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Strategic and operational support for the Director Expansion&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Own and execute individual projects such as analysis of the various types of data and target market, hands-on roll-out of new practices and many more&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Setting up, question and further develop existing processes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Contribute to Avi Medical’s open and empowering culture!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
